<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="del-2020-03-crypt"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>Deleted items for month 2020-03</title></titleStmt><publicationStmt><p>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</p></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><p>Created by members of the TLS project</p></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation>Initially created: <date>2020-03-24T15:19:10.603+09:00</date>.</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Deleted items</head><p xml:id="del-2020-03-start"><seg corresp="#CH2b1913_CHANT_127-16a.253" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2020-03-24T15:19:10.603+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="CH2b1913-en">Just look here!</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T00:34:16.861+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">Now, concerning the fact that the teachings of the Confucians are transmitted, whereas the laws of the Mohists are not,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-1a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T01:22:45.003+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">Given that the spirits do not constist of dead people's essence,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-1a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T01:22:47.202+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">Given that spirits do not constist of dead people's essence,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-1a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T01:25:01.473+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">Now the Mohist school claims that spirits do indeed consist of dead people's essence,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-1a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T01:44:13.842+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">and even if one would worship them,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-1a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T01:54:50.505+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">in order to serve the spirits and requests blessings</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-1a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T02:02:13.966+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">If one measures all by one</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T02:03:01.26+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">Now, concerning the fact that the teachings of the Confucians are transmitted, whereas the laws of the Mohists are not,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T02:03:09.796+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">whereas the laws and discussions of the Mohists are difficult to implement.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-1a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T02:07:00.589+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">the Mohist school designed its methods</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-1a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T02:51:40.012+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">all in this way.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-1a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T02:52:55.438+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">in this way.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-1a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T02:53:07.248+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">seems to be justified.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-2a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T03:08:18.375+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">Guliang Zhi</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-2a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T03:12:56.127+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">Liu Zizheng [i.e. Liu Xiang] studied 'Mr Zuo's (Tradition)'</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-2a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T04:35:38.062+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">putting forward (a number of texts, thereby establishing) right and wrong,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-2a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T05:16:49.157+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">and Fan Sheng's memorials were (thereby) refuted,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-2a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T05:16:58.11+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">and Fan Sheng's memorials were refuted,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-2a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T05:29:26.412+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">highly contradicts (the fact that) Master Kong did not discuss strange things and brute force</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-2a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T05:37:06.715+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">where great talents of the empire,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-2a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T06:22:13.407+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">Chen Yuan's word were plain,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-2a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T06:25:45.042+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">putting forward (a number of) passages, (discussing) right and wrong,</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-2a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-25T06:26:15.42+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">with great vigour.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-7a.59" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T00:02:25.704+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">All those that I have proposed</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-7a.54" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T00:09:30.586+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Your mother's younger brother Gōngsūn Jìchéng</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-7a.61" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T00:11:58.236+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">How can I have hopes to rise as far as the prime ministership of Wèi.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-7a.67" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T00:15:31.551+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">You will be next in line."</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-7a.67" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T01:24:19.593+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">You will be next in line, in the end."</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-8a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T01:33:24.355+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">he told his entourage:</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-8a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T05:20:08.347+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">The attendant said:</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-8a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T05:22:37.582+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Your Majesty should ask for an explanation from him.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-8a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T05:36:44.052+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">I have promote Tián Jiězǐ to govern Nánchéng, and the Chǔ offered their allegiance at your court with rolls of silk.</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-2a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-27T20:03:28.384+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-1f298121">wheres those of Gongyang GAo</seg><seg corresp="#KR3j0080_tls_083-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#paulfahr" modified="2020-03-27T20:12:10.572+09:00" resp-del="#paulfahr" src-id="KR3j0080-en-a19da179">What means 'jia' in this context?</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-03-27T20:15:21.96+09:00" resp-del="#wilke" src-id="CH1a0907-de-b4e888c1">Who is the Duke of Jin?!</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#wilke" modified="2020-03-27T20:42:41.904+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="CH1a0907-de-b4e888c1"> </seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T21:05:40.31+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-de-b4e888c1">he noticed that Bó Lǐxī's oxen were well-fed</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T21:08:32.431+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-de-b4e888c1">When there was danger I personally protected them from in front and from behind,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T21:13:20.249+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-de-b4e888c1">The Duke was greatly pleased withBó Lǐxī.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T21:14:27.112+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-de-b4e888c1">and I've been deploying them without recklessnes.</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>